{"tid":2451723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"作品被容海恩指對國家不敬　艾未未回應指容海恩不懂及不理解藝術","createTime":"2021-03-18T10:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T16:30:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"58ed65c5d3ae3828d5825e4524c4f22860e0aedb","tid":2451723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:01:35.000Z","msg":"新民黨立法會議員容海恩不滿，西九文化區「M+博物館」展出一幅藝術家艾未未作品，相中人以中指指向北京天安門廣場，強調M+博物館以公帑建造，沒理由展示對國家不敬的作品。<br />\n<br />\n艾未未有關系列作品，亦有向美國白宮、伯恩聯邦議會大廈等舉起中指。艾未未接受本台訪問時表示，作為立法會議員，將藝術範疇視為與政治對抗，是對藝術不理解，若只將藝術理解為裝飾品，這並不懂得藝術，強調藝術的核心價值就是提出問題以及對權威的質疑。<br />\n<br />\n艾未未形容，對事件感到遺憾，但同時亦有點興奮，為他在當今藝術史上投了贊同票。他又說，有關作品是瑞士前駐華大使烏利希克的其中收藏品，烏利希克其後將大部分收藏品捐贈「M+博物館」，而烏利希克與中國關係很好，相信今次事件亦對他帶來巨大衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581333-20210318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581333-20210318.htm&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2XQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=6a1c3d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581333-20210318.htm&h=f21e6c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581333-20210318.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8b66f3bb3dd0873dfa5710af3df4fd33ee3cc2c7","tid":2451723,"uid":52779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以唔好柒"},{"pid":"721480ee53b03eea1233b421e8b17b793a65ba15","tid":2451723,"uid":191453,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74WoXb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74WoXb8.jpg&h=59d42b3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6542a34b0518c422eb28594d8298280f28c1d8d","tid":245172